<item>
            <title>[LU-19422] pool quota recalculation works only for all quota types(ugp).</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-19422</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Pool quotas recalculation works only when all quota types are enabled(enabled=ugp). Otherwise, even if only one or two types are enabled qmt_pool_recalc() stops recalculation and returns -EINVAL. As a result Pool Quotas may have insane granted space resulting in a wrong -EDQUOT.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
